data.description: Get ready to relax and live the easy life! This home sits towards the end of the street, across from a neighborhood greenspace and walking distance to the pool. Homeowners Association takes care of front and back lawncare so that you can enjoy the finer things! Stepless front entry to the foyer that opens to a gorgeous living space. A comfortable Family Room where you can relax by the fireplace; with ease of access to the light-filled kitchen and separate dining room. The perfect combo of Master Suite and laundry on the main level. Upstairs you'll find 3 additional bedrooms, 1 full bathroom, and a loft space - perfect for lounging, an office space, teen media room or kid's playroom. Cozy courtyard-like back patio great for grilling and dining outside. Brand new dishwasher, roof is only 5 years old, new AC unit (08/23), Berber carpet. Convenient to I-985, Lake Lanier, shopping and dining.
